data.description: Located in desirable Lake Charles Community in St. Lucie West, this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with a 2 car garage is waiting for you. CBS construction with a NEW 2024 tile roof and newly painted exterior. Over 2100 square feet of open concept, spacious living. A large 16 x 13 kitchen with high gloss white cabinets offers room for the option of adding a table for informal dining.The formal living room & dining room area is a great space for entertaining, with a family room off the kitchen for kicking back to relax and watch tv.A spacious screen room area off the back looks out into the private back yard with lush tropical landscaping. Call today for your private showing.
